latestIgtvVideos.caption: Black Friday is finally here! ✨#EsteeTeam @krisnewbeauty gives you a closer look at our favorite, best-selling products to help you pamper yourself or your loved ones during this holiday season 💕 Tap to watch and learn more.

Indulge in some sweet #selfgifting this season and treat your skin to the 72-hour hydration of our number one #AdvancedNightRepair serum. Tap to shop and power through the holidays with radiant skin. #GiftsToDelight

Gift silky-soft skin to someone special on your list ✨. Deeply nourishing #RevitalizingSupreme unlocks skin’s youth potential so that it springs back with new bounce and radiance. Tap to shop! #EsteeWishlist #GiftsToDelight
#EsteeArtist @bobbiewu_makeup here to remind you take off your Halloween look using Advanced Micro Cleansing Balm it removes all makeup—plus those spooky impurities. ✨ #HappyHalloween 🎃

When we formulated #AdvancedNightRepair Serum, we had no idea ghosts would want to get their hands on it, too! 👻 Don’t miss out on getting your bottle. Tap to shop and have a bootiful Halloween! 🌕 #HappyHalloween

Emmy-nominated actress and singer @mjrodriguez7 rocks the best beauty beat for a friend’s wedding with the help of a few of her Estée Lauder faves: #AdvancedNightRepair Serum, #DoubleWear Stay-in-Place Foundation and #PureColor Whipped Matte Liquid Lip Color.
